				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">First off, if your not Rallos, your not hardcore. (as far as pvp goes)
<br />

<br />
I would definatly go with Ogre for the no frontal stun, this although might not be as useful in pvp, is great in pve.
<br />

<br />
When i made my Ogre beastlord i put 5 in agi or dex so that they would both be 75, and the rest in wisdom.  The most important thing though is to decide wether you a pk or antipk. imho beastlords make the best lvl 9 pks (for those who dont know, lvl 9 is the last level where people cannot loot an item off you), because they can blind, have pets (no guard agro), and hit for as much as anyone els in melee at lvl 9. 
<br />

<br />
The main difference though in pvp, is that ogres can slam, and iksars cant. My main on Rallos is a cleric, and i cant tell you how frusterating it is to people when i pull off a complete heal while being beaten on.
<br />

<br />
If you are going with the iksar, just make sure your ready to take a few days to hit lvl 16+ in FoB.<br />_________________<br />In the life of many arggs, only those with the biggest arggs, live to tell another argg.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
