				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Adding wisdom is always a no brainer for beastlords. I would stick the rest in sta also.
<br />

<br />
On tallon you'll have to choose a team to play, your race will effect what team you're on.
<br />

<br />
Ogre, Troll, Iksar - Dark team
<br />
Barb, Vah Shir - Blue team.
<br />

<br />
There are 2 other teams on tall/vallon, but Bst can't be either, they're peck team and elf team. Race won't make much of a difference with pvp, being an ogre and unstunnable might be nice.
