Being able to take the law into your own hands on a red server and killing someone to take the camp/mob/raid is the same as when blue servers take the law into their hands and KS, Train, Lag out the other players/raids, only with less experience loss. Just because you took the camp within the confines of the PVP abilities to do so doesn't make it anymore right.
<br />

